          <p class='first-para'>
            Would there not then be a confusion of responsibility if the child is being looked after by its parents and by the local authority? Who actually is in charge?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0564P0-04702'>
        <a name='S5LV0564P0_19950606_GCR_215'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-peter-fraser' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
