        <span class="member">Lord Fraser of Carmyllie</span> moved Amendment No. 39:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0564P0-04737'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0564P0_19950606_GCR_250' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
