          <p class='first-para'>
            Once again we seem to have reached a point where I wish to be explicit and the noble and learned Lord the Minister wishes to be implicit. Again, I take the point that one could have to make too wide a plan. Therefore, I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0564P0-04774'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0564P0_19950606_GCR_287' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0564P0-04775'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0564P0_19950606_GCR_288' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
