        Page 16, line 40, at end insert&#x2014;
        <q>("( ) Every local authority shall make such provision as they consider appropriate for the following services to be available with respect to children in need within their area while they are living with their families&#x2014;
        <ol>
        <li>(a) advice, guidance and counselling;</li>
        <li>(b) occupational, social, cultural or recreational activities;</li>
        <li>(c) home help (which may include laundry facilities);</li>
