        Clause 23 [<span class="italic">Manner of provision of accommodation to child looked after by local authority</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0564P0-04941'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0564P0_19950606_GCR_454' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
